gfxboot-turnkey notes
=====================

- 16x16.fnt, boot.cat, gfxboot.c32, vesamenu.c32

    - pulled in from ubuntu iso (oneric)
    - could possibly just get them from devel environment (see below)

- isolinux.cfg, gfxboot.cfg, menu.cfg, lang, splash.pcx

    - custom made for turnkey

- bootlogo, en.tr

    - cd minimal (squeeze)
    - fab-chroot build/root.tmp
    - apt-get install gfxboot gfxboot-dev make wget
    - wget .../gfxboot-theme-ubuntu_0.12.2.tar.gz, unpack

    - cd gfxboot-theme-ubuntu
    - rm po/*.po
    - hack panel.inc (see diff below, remove all F* except F6)
    - hack dia_fulloptions.inc (see diff below, rename option, remove options)

    - make
    - copy out install/{bootlogo, en.tr}


